5 September 2015The Inter-Ministerial Committee (IMC) on migration led by Minister for Performance, Monitoring and Evaluation in the Presidency, Jeff Radebe will hold a media briefing to provide an update on its work including Operation Fiela.Details of the briefing are as follows:Date: Monday, 7 September 2015 Time: 09h00 Venue: GCIS, Tshedimosetso House, Corner Francis Baard and Festival streets, Hatfield PretoriaNB: There will be a video link to Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, and Parliament in Cape TownRSVP: Ireen Magwai (Pretoria) Cell: 082 440 5676 Andile Duka (Cape Town) Cell: 071 154 4519 Enquiries: Acting Cabinet Spokesperson Phumla Williams Cell: 083 501 0139Issued by: GCIS